collections.name: Axum nft studio
collections.description:
Axum NFT Studio is a cutting-edge digital art studio specializing in the creation, curation, and sale of unique and innovative NFTs (Non-Fungible Tokens). Our vision is to empower artists and collectors alike by bringing groundbreaking and exclusive digital assets to the blockchain. We blend artistry with technology to craft visually stunning, one-of-a-kind pieces that represent the future of creativity in the digital world.

At Axum NFT Studio, we believe in the transformative power of NFTs to redefine ownership, value, and art in the digital age. Each collection is carefully curated, with a focus on originality, quality, and the cultural impact of our creations. Whether you're a collector seeking the next iconic piece or an artist looking to bring your vision to the blockchain, Axum NFT Studio is your go-to destination for premium, avant-garde digital art.

Join us on our journey as we continue to innovate and shape the future of the NFT space, offering exclusive drops, collaboration

collections.name: Ape Days
collections.description:
APE DAYS is a passion project that was first conceived in September 2021 by Artist itscullyn.
Originally inspired by the energy and vibes behind the NFT community from 2021 through 2022 while spending time hanging out in early spaces and sifting through discord servers.
This hand painted collection brings together 250 traits, adapted for - among others - four expressions, three skin tones and two variations of fur. This was done in an attempt to bring more variation and diversity of choice beyond the mint.
This project is being delivered complete, no broken promises, for the art, CC0.

collections.name: Creagnos
collections.description:
Creagnos reflects our perspective on the dynamic relationship between human intelligence and artificial intelligence; Each piece in this collection presents a step-by-step narrative of our view on this subject.
The collection represents a snapshot of the synthesis between the philosophy of technology and the history of human civilization- a visual discourse connecting the past, present and future.

This collection focuses on the potential costs that artificial intelligence may bring in the evolution of human civilization, where humans are both the subject and the object.

As an NFT artwork and an asset, Creagnos strives for purity and innovation to maintain its value- conceptually, visually, and linguistically.

collections.name: Art Tembe
collections.description:
L’art Tembé est une forme d’expression artistique traditionnelle des Bushinengués (descendants d’esclaves africains ayant trouvé refuge en Guyane, au Suriname et au Brésil). Il se caractérise par des motifs géométriques colorés et entrelacés, chargés de symboles et de significations profondes.

Origines et Signification
L’art Tembé est historiquement lié à la culture Aluku, Ndyuka et Saramaka. À l’origine, il servait à décorer des objets du quotidien (pagaies, portes, coffres, bijoux, textiles) et à transmettre des messages codés entre initiés. Chaque motif raconte une histoire et reflète les valeurs de la communauté :

L’harmonie et la connexion avec la nature
L’unité et la transmission intergénérationnelle
La résilience face aux épreuves
Caractéristiques Visuelles
Des formes géométriques complexes (triangles, spirales, lignes entrelacées)
Des couleurs vives et contrastées (rouge, bleu, jaune, vert)
Un style dynamique et rythmé, souvent

collections.name: Elements of the Heart
collections.description: “Elements of the Heart” is an NFT series that explores the symbolism of the human heart in different states and elements. From blazing fire to crystalline ice, each piece represents a distinct emotion and inner strength. This collection seeks to unite art and feeling, showcasing how the heart can take on multiple forms—whether mechanical, natural, luminous, or even corrupted. Each NFT is unique and carries its own narrative, inviting the collector to reflect on the essence of life, emotions, and creativity.
